OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FCloudier
OL,6,Fon Friday, dry at first but with the
OL,7,Fchance of some showery rain later,
OL,8,Fperhaps heavy. Saturday cloudy and
OL,9,Fcooler. Brighter with some sunshine on
OL,10,FSunday, but still cooler.
